-- Alitalia Chief Sabelli Favors Merger With Air France from 2013, Ansa Says
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2010-11-02T12:52:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/alitalia-chief-sabelli-favors-merger-with-air-france-from-2013-ansa-says.html
Alitalia SpA Chief Executive Officer
Rocco Sabelli favors a merger of the Italian airline with Air
France-KLM Group from 2013, Ansa reported quoting from a preview
of a book by journalist Bruno Vespa, which cites Sabelli.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
